data.description: Excellent opportunity to own a well cared for home w/ many upgrades in James Landing.  Almost 3000 sf. of living area, w/ great outdoor natural area privacy in backyard, for you to enjoy on your spacious deck. Home is designed to be enjoyed, whether in the modern kitchen, window walled sunroom or warm & inviting den w/ fireplace, you're going to love to call this home, your home.  Want a more formal setting? The living room & dining room present just what you need; beautiful hardwood floors & plantation blinds you're sure to appreciate. Kitchen upgrades (2019) include cabinets, farmhouse sink, lighting, appliances, granite countertop & more; sunroom ceramic floor (2019) & windows (2023); new roof (2019), pvc sewage pipes (2018), electric water heater (2022) & much more. Please see attached extensive list from seller for additional upgrades.
